## Change Log

0.12.5
======

- [#1370](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1370) Make slide work after Android device rotation. (@ChristianMayer)
- [#1363](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1363) entries in cv.Config.configSettings.stylesToLoad  can be objects {urlo… (@peuter)

0.12.4
======

- [#1353](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1353) fixes icon cache error (@peuter)

0.12.3
======

- [#1344](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1344) use root here, because it always exists. Possible fix for sentry erroh… (@peuter)

0.12.2
======

- [#1339](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1339) Cherry picking fixes for web-widget and speech plugin (@peuter)
- [#1313](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1313) Do not process influx data by backend processors, because it is alreal… (@peuter)

0.12.1
======

- [#1290](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1290) check for openhab environent and php support. (@peuter)

0.12.0
======

### v0.12.0-RC12 (2022/05/11)

- [#1277](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1278) set navbars to inactive before bailing out (@peuter)

### v0.12.0-RC11 (2022/05/11)

- [#1277](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1277) only skip if the navbar has a scope set (@peuter)

### v0.12.0-RC10 (2022/05/11)

- [#1276](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1276) Fix 2d pages. (@ChristianMayer)
- [#1274](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1274) Bump grunt from 1.4.1 to 1.5.2 (@dependabot[bot])
- [#1275](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1275) Fix navbar on subpages where it is not inherited anymore. (@ChristianMayer)
- [#1273](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1273) Update documentation according to user feedback (@ChristianMayer)
- [#1270](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1270) update file content after save (@peuter)
- [#1272](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1272) Bump axios from 0.21.1 to 0.21.4 (@dependabot[bot])
- [#1269](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1269) Enhance english documentation of clock plugin. (@ChristianMayer)
- [#1271](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1271) Bump simple-git from 3.3.0 to 3.5.0 in /.github/actions/github (@dependabot[bot])
- [#1267](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1267) replace some special characters in attribute values (@peuter)
- [#1265](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1265) Use more standard mechanism to fix mobile firefox. (@ChristianMayer)
- [#1264](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1264) Enhance MQTT transfom documentation (@ChristianMayer)
- [#1261](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1261) use space as clearfix content, fixes layout problem in chrome (@peuter)
- [#1262](https://github.com/CometVisu/CometVisu/pull/1262) fix configuration upgrader process (@peuter)

